# Agent OS — environment
# Secrets are namespaced by tenant + principal so brands are isolated:
#   <TENANT>__<PRINCIPAL>__<KEY>   (double underscore separators)
# Example: a service account `svc-billing` for tenant `acme` needing a Stripe key:
#   ACME__SVC_BILLING__STRIPE_API_KEY=sk_live_...
#
# The Secrets vault never hands the raw key to the agent — capabilities read it
# inside the gateway boundary only.

# AGENT_OS_AUDIT_DIR=./data/audit
